{"word":"Health-Disease","slug":"health-disease","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Health-Disease</b> - <b>(A) HEALTH,</b> promised to the obedient<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=26'>Exo 15:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=7&verse=15'>Deu 7:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=4&verse=22'>Pro 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=30&verse=17'>Jer 30:17</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Immunity, ISRAEL-THE JEWS<p/><b>(B) DISEASE,</b> different forms of<p/><b>(1) Boils</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=9'>Exo 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=18'>Lev 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=7'>2Ki 20:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=2&verse=7'>Job 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=21'>Isa 38:21</a><p/><b>(2) Epilepsy</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=24'>Mat 4:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=14'>Mat 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=15'>Mat 17:15</a><p/><b>(3) Fever</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=16'>Lev 26:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=28&verse=22'>Deu 28:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=30&verse=30'>Job 30:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=30'>Mar 1:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=52'>Joh 4:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=8'>Act 28:8</a><p/><b>(4) Insanity</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=33'>Dan 4:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibl