=11&verse=1'>Joh 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=37'>Act 9:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=2&verse=27'>Phi 2:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=20'>2Ti 4:20</a><p/><b>(D) BODILY INFIRMITIES, </b>general references to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=17'>Mat 8:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=15'>Luk 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=11'>Luk 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=5'>Joh 5:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=10'>2Co 12:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=4&verse=13'>Gal 4:13</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=23'>1Ti 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=4&verse=15'>Heb 4:15</a><p/>For Deafness, See DEAFNESS<p/>--The Dumb, See 1541<p/><b>(E) BLINDNESS</b><p/><b>(1) Physical, </b>inflicted<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=11'>Gen 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=18'>2Ki 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=8'>Act 9:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=11'>Act 13:11</a><p/><b>(2) Healed</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=27'>Mat 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=22'>Mat 12:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=20&verse=30'>Mat 20:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=14'>Mat 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=22'>Mar 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=46'>Mar 10:46</a>; <